=Description=

"How ... are co-operatives adapting to the digital revolution? ... This study looks in detail at how co-operatives are using digital tools. Based on an online questionnaire answered by co-operatives across the world, and in-depth interviews with leaders in a range of co-operative business sectors, we uncover how co-operatives are using digital tools, and make comparisons with non-co-operative competitors."

